ext":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25107,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/07\/24\/urwah-no-iman-cannot-trust\/","url_meta":{"origin":37579,"position":2},"title":"Urwah on Trust: No faith for one who cannot be trusted","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham ibn 'Urwah reported: 'Urwah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cBe not deceived by the prayer of a man, nor by his fasting. Whoever wills can fast and whoever wills can pray, yet there is no religion for one who cannot be trusted.\u201d Source: al-\u012ama\u0304n li Ibn Abi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8167,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/prophet-encourages-huriyyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37579,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Freedom: The Prophet encourages freeing slaves, prisoners","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said to Abu al-Haytham, \u201cDo you have a servant?\u201d He said no. The Prophet said, \u201cIf we receive prisoners of war, come to us.\u201d Then, the Prophet had with him two prisoners. He came and the Prophet said, \u201cChoose\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33950,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/27\/five-deeds-to-enter-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37579,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Five deeds for the faithful to enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever comes with five deeds, along with faith, will enter Paradise: one who preserves the five prayers, their ablution, their bowings, their prostrations, and their timings, who fasts the month of Ramadan, who performs Hajj pilgrimage\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6014,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/07\/key-salat-wudu-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37579,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Key to Paradise is prayer, ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe key to Paradise is prayer, and the key to prayer is ablution.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 4 Grade:\u00a0Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 